# TS Imports And Layout

- Use `@/*` aliases for cross-folder imports.
- Use `./` imports inside the same folder.
- Avoid parent-relative imports (`../`) when `@/*` is appropriate.
- Prefer `interface` for contracts and `type` for unions/aliases.
- Re-export public APIs through `index.ts` barrel files.
- Keep module order consistent: imports -> exports/types -> constants/schemas -> factory -> helpers.
